Class IntBetweenRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.terma.fastselect.Request
      • com.github.terma.fastselect.ColumnRequest
        • com.github.terma.fastselect.IntBetweenRequest

  • public class IntBetweenRequest
extends ColumnRequest
    SQL analog is COLUMN_X >= MIN and COLUMN_X <= MAX

    Math's analog is "a to []". Include min and max.

    For equal select use IntRequest
